 facility features spacious exercise zones, New York pet care professionals, offering pet care. Their services creates a safe, climate-controlled environment. centrally located for Newburgh residents. Reach out to Pet Pro for a consultation\",\"slug\":\"pet-pro\",\"address\":\"1606 NY-82\",\"street\":\"1606 NY-82\",\"city\":\"Newburgh\",\"state\":\"NY\",\"zipCode\":\"12540\",\"full_address\":\"1606 NY-82, Lagrangeville, NY 12540, USA\",\"latitude\":41.6273104,\"longitude\":-73.77171009999999,\"googlePlaceId\":\"ChIJjTRUv2dB3YkRQ-c-P0e6ZNo\",\"phone\":\"(845) 226-8335\",\"rating\":4.4,\"reviewCount\":68,\"userRatingsTotal\":68,\"pricing\":{\"pricingSource\":\"unknown\",\"isFree\":false},\"placeTypes\":[\"point_of_interest\",\"establishment\"],\"dataQuality\":\"verified\",\"openingHours\":{\"Monday\":\"9:00 AM – 7:00 PM\",\"Tuesday\":\"9:00 AM – 7:00 PM\",\"Wednesday\":\"9:00 AM – 7:00 PM\",\"Thursday\":\"9:00 AM – 7:00 PM\",\"Friday\":\"9:00 AM – 7:00 PM\",\"Saturday\":\"9:00 AM – 7:00 PM\",\"Sunday\":\"9:00 AM – 5:00 PM\"},\"faqs\":[],\"amenities\":{},\"photos\":[{\"url\":\"/images/parks/newyork/pet-pro/pet-pro-1.jpg\",\"type\":\"photo\",\"source\":\"website\"},{\"url\":\"/images/parks/newyork/pet-pro/pet-pro-2.jpg\",\"type\":\"photo\",\"source\":\"website\"}],\"photo\":\"/images/parks/newyork/pet-pro/pet-pro-1.jpg\",\"source\":\"static\",\"listingType\":\"free\"}}]\n3f:[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-8 text-center\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"$L13\",null,{\"href\":\"/\",\"className\":\"inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 bg-purple-600 text-white rounded-md hover:bg-purple-700 transition-colors font-medium\",\"children\":\"Browse All Parks →\"}]}]\n40:[\"$\",\"i\",null,{\"className\":\"bi bi-geo-alt mr-2\"}]\n41:[\"$\",\"$L13\",\"eads\",{\"href\":\"/cities/eads\",\"className\":\"inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 bg-white text-purple-700 rounded-lg hover:bg-purple-50 transition-colors font-medium shadow-sm\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"i\",null,{\"className\":\"bi bi-g